  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0da9\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d94\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The student who went to the sports competition was killed in Deduru Oya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A sixteen-year-old student studying at Gonigoda Maha Vidyalaya, who went swimming in Deduru Oye without going home while returning from participating in a school sports tournament, has died due to drowning, according to the Ridhigama police.",
        "A student named Kavindu Rashmit Jayasuriya, who was studying in the 11th year of the school, has died. He is the eldest child in a family of two children in Gokarella Polgolla area.",
        "A group of students of this school along with a group of teachers went to Gokarella area to participate in an athletics tournament held between schools belonging to the Ibbagamuwa Education Zone and after participating in the tournament, the group of students along with the teachers returned home the same day.",
        "The group had come home in a lorry and on the way, after the group of teachers got off the lorry, only the remaining students traveled there.",
        "The police said that only the three students who were involved in the accident did not go directly to their homes but got off the lorry on the way and went to bathe near the Ogodapola Mahawela Bridge in Deduru Oye which flows through the area.",
        "Two of the three who went into the water drowned at once and somehow one of the students managed to escape and reach the shore, but the other student is missing after drowning. Later, the local residents brought the student's body to the ground and admitted him to the Gonigoda Rural Hospital, but he was already dead."
      ],
